sub_title: Customer Advisor, HR business Partner and Entrepreneur(English Institution)
summary:
My career has had me wearing many hats, and I have developed extensive experience in three fields. 
First, I have worked as a Human Resources specialist in the car industry and fintech start-up businesses. Second, I was a customer acquisition coordinator at different English Institutions. 
Third, I have taught English in Iran and Canada. I have great patience in facing people. I'm trying my best to do all my duties. I love to learn more, and searching is still sticking in my lifestyle. Having completed a major in Business Management, I am familiar with many subjects related to customer services and management concepts. My eagerness and desire to be creative and innovative made me start my own business based on my English knowledge and management. I established an English Institution in Iran and still working as a manager and an English teacher.  I am inquisitive and focused on personal and professional learning in all aspects of life. All my positions allowed me to be strong in time-management skills and demonstrate my organizational skills. I am keenly interested in the Human Resources area of studies and work. I have completed several online courses with the IPM Association, Canada's critical professional recruiter's association.
